sonal Savvy. Business Acumen. We like people who aren’t afraid to stand alone, who deal with ambiguity instead of ignoring it and who know how to approach any problem, no matter how difficult. If you have these qualities, and are committed to making the most of your talents, you’ll fit right in here.   Qualifications:Studying towards a Bachelors or a Masters, with focus on marketing and ideally relevant practical experience through qualified internships or similar in the country or abroad.Strong communication skills, analytical skills, goal-oriented approach and numbers affinity. A high degree of creativity, initiative and enthusiasm for working with brands.Fun at the independent, organized and varied work.Fluent in German and English, as well as computer literacy (MS Office)At Mondelēz International, we want you to thrive. That’s why we foster a culture in which people believe in each other and want to grow together. One in which you’re given the chance to lead and have your ideas heard, but also in which you’re encouraged to help others too.*Are you interested in the role of the Marketing Praktikum / Internship? Please send an up-to-date CV via the APPLY now!* 



 



